{"tid":836630,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"強逼症係咪好唔返","createTime":"2018-09-25T20:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T10:48:39.000Z","uid":16535,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1d578f58399c83530ba91375b86c0992b90eb9","tid":836630,"uid":16535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:17:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>強迫思想是指不斷重複的思想，患者雖然知道這些思想是多餘的、不理性的，但卻阻止不了這些思想的出現，不斷侵入患者思想的想法和觀念，並覺得非常厭惡，強迫症患者頻繁地重複做某件事情（強迫行為）則是為了緩解由於強迫觀念而產生的焦慮情緒。</strong><br />\n<br />\n反反覆覆六七年，掂到某樣野就要洗手，洗幾次洗到隻手又紅又乾，長期買消毒濕紙巾，屋企人由一開始鬧打嘈到唔理，同事問做咩隻手長期咁乾，有口難言，個世界唔會有人明。<br />\n<br />\n鐘意人都唔敢拍拖覺得自己係怪人，好想死，自殺念頭不斷出現，真係好痛苦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4f559624a0efbbb5dc16178c8aec5883fe87d9","tid":836630,"uid":63843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:24:15.000Z","msg":"焦慮症?"},{"pid":"c5d4b59b907b88a1443c83752b8dc0dee97dc093","tid":836630,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:26:25.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"08dcb8dd76ba1cc7cba7c21fd31be521fc90058e","tid":836630,"uid":210139,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:30:52.000Z","msg":"唔似只係强迫症<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ebe82bead031e2259fcef2ab9e62af19bd47cc","tid":836630,"uid":16535,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"9e4f559624a0efbbb5dc16178c8aec5883fe87d9","tid":836630,"uid":63843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:24:15.000Z","msg":"焦慮症?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"強逼症已經係焦慮症既一種"},{"pid":"240fbaace6fa483788a7320efc738b5f11791d1a","tid":836630,"uid":16535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08dcb8dd76ba1cc7cba7c21fd31be521fc90058e","tid":836630,"uid":210139,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:30:52.000Z","msg":"唔似只係强迫症<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim